(642, 1, '2013-04-17 16:45:28', '2013-04-17 14:45:28', 'Hlengiwe Skosana has been appointed as Performance Improvement Consultant at OIM, one of South Africas leading business performance specialists. Skosana will offer employee relations (ER) services at the company.\r\n\r\nSkosana is an International Labour Organisation (ILO) accreditedcommissioner trained in arbitration, mediation, conciliation labour legislation and conflict management. She has extensive experience in labour relations and conflict resolution.\r\n\r\nSkosana co-founded D-Vine Interventions, and worked as a mediator and arbitrator for the CCMA, Public Health and Welfare Bargaining Council as well as the Public Service Bargaining Council.', 'New appointment Hlengiwe Skosana', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-appointment-hlengiwe-skosana', '', '', '2013-10-17 16:46:01', '2013-10-17 14:46:01', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.11/OIM/website-wp/htdocs/?p=642', 0, 'post', '', 0),
