(646, 1, '2013-04-15 16:46:40', '2013-04-15 14:46:40', 'Jaco van der Merwe has been appointed as Performance Improvement Consultant at OIM, one of South Africas leading business performance specialists. Van der Merwe will facilitate workshops and skills development programmes, as well as coaching clients on the implementation of OIMs performance improvement methodology.\r\n\r\nWith a BProc degree, Van der Merwe is skilled in the areas of stakeholder engagement, legislative compliance, risk management, project management as well as process re-engineering and optimisation. He brings with him experience in leading training initiatives in the retail banking sector.\r\n\r\nVan der Merwe spent 13 years at Absa, where he began his career as a project manager, and before joining OIM, was working as a regional training consultant.', 'New appointment Jaco van der Merwe', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-appointment-jaco-van-der-merwe', '', '', '2013-10-17 16:47:09', '2013-10-17 14:47:09', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.11/OIM/website-wp/htdocs/?p=646', 0, 'post', '', 0),
