(648, 1, '2013-04-15 16:47:24', '2013-04-15 14:47:24', 'Kevin Setzkorn has recently been appointed as Operation Solutions Consultant at OIM, one of South Africas leading business performance specialists. Setzkorn will be consulting on supervisory development projects at the company as well as providing on-the-floor coaching to supervisors.\r\n\r\nPreviously, Setzkorn practised as a climate change and sustainability advisor at KPMG Services, where he worked with companies such as Implats, Eskom, BHP Billiton, Gold Fields and Standard Bank.\r\n\r\nWith a Bachelor of Science Honours in Geography and currently completing his Master of Sciences in Engineering, Setzkorn brings with him the following skills to his new position: Non-financial auditing, sustainability reporting, Global Reporting Initiative (GRI) benchmarking, lean methodology and coaching on operational efficiency.', 'New appointment Kevin Setzkorn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-appointment-kevin-setzkorn', '', '', '2013-10-17 16:47:50', '2013-10-17 14:47:50', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.11/OIM/website-wp/htdocs/?p=648', 0, 'post', '', 0),
