(721, 1, '2013-10-22 09:45:35', '2013-10-22 07:45:35', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-323" alt="OIM Umbono Mining Solutions" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/umbono.gif" width="164" height="44" />\r\n\r\nOIM Umbono Mining Solutions is a joint venture between OIM and Umbono Capital, combining the unique skills and experience of the two companies to unlock operational efficiency in the mining industry.\r\n\r\nVisit <a href="http://www.oimumbono.com/" target="_blank">www.oimumbono.com</a> and <a href="http://www.umbono.com/" target="_blank">www.umbono.com</a> for more information.\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-325" alt="Pure Survey" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/pure.gif" width="222" height="37" />\r\n\r\nAs one of South Africas leaders on online surveys for customers, employees and market research, we have partnered with Pure Survey to provide affordable, innovative and effective stakeholder perception surveys. Surveys are customised for each clients unique needs and the main goal is useful reporting and data analysis that you, as the customer, require to effectively measure and manage your environment.\r\n\r\nVisit <a href="http://www.puresurvey.co.za/" target="_blank">www.puresurvey.co.za</a> for more information.\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>\r\nIn offering our leadership assessment and development interventions we have teamed up with several leading international talent management houses.\r\n<div style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-326" alt="Saville Consulting" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/saville.gif" width="265" height="36" />\r\n\r\nSaville Consulting develops rigorous and work-relevant assessment tools that measure the critical fit between individuals, job requirements and workplace culture.\r\n\r\nFor more information on this leader in its field, visit <a href="http://www.savilleconsulting.co.za" target="_blank">www.savilleconsulting.co.za.</a>\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-327" alt="Shl" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/shl.gif" width="76" height="47" />\r\n\r\nShl, a global leader in talent measurement, offers employment testing tools and employee development assessment services.\r\n\r\nVisit <a href="http://www.shl.com/" target="_blank">www.shl.com</a> for information on their extensive solutions and expertise.\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-328" alt="Insights" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/insights.gif" width="63" height="75" />\r\n\r\nEveryone who has ever worked in a team-driven environment understands the importance of solid relations and work methods to get things done.\r\n\r\nWith Insights international track record spanning 20 years, we use the Insights methodology to improve team effectiveness at our clients. It helps people to learn about themselves and others in a practical, results-driven way using colours and fun exercises.\r\n\r\nRead more about this methodology and case studies at <a href="http://www.insights.com" target="_blank">www.insights.com.</a>\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>', 'Partnerships', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '320-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-22 09:45:35', '2013-10-22 07:45:35', '', 320, 'http://localhost/oim_wp/htdocs/news/uncategorized/320-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
